'''ISO 3166-2:BG'''
is an [[International Organization for Standardization | ISO]] standard which defines [[geocode]]s: it is the subset of [[ISO 3166-2]] which applies to
[[Bulgaria]].

The [[Provinces of Bulgaria|provinces]] (''oblasti'', singular - ''[[oblast]]'') are numbered according to their position in the Bulgarian alphabet.

